00:19:25,729 --> 00:19:27,145
and kind of backed off.

388
00:19:27,145 --> 00:19:29,147
Is that it?

389
00:19:29,147 --> 00:19:30,429
Yeah.

390
00:19:30,429 --> 00:19:32,529
It was the same with you, wasn't it, Officer Takagi,

391
00:19:32,529 --> 00:19:34,329
