392
00:19:34,329 --> 00:19:36,729
No, in my case...

393
00:19:38,429 --> 00:19:40,029
Kiss me.

394
00:19:40,029 --> 00:19:41,529
Right now.

395
00:19:41,529 --> 00:19:42,929
A hot passionate one.

396
00:19:43,929 --> 00:19:47,929
I see. She said so, because it was me.

397
00:19:47,929 --> 00:19:50,529
Officer Sato said so, because it was me.

398
00:19:59,177 --> 00:20:01,179
We've finally found the residence

399
00:20:01,179 --> 00:20:03,929
