400
00:20:03,929 --> 00:20:06,429
"First Investigation Division" -It's on the 2nd floor of a pachinko parlor

401
00:20:06,429 --> 00:20:08,529
in Okuhocho 3-chome.

402
00:20:08,529 --> 00:20:09,729
According to the information we have,

403
00:20:09,729 --> 00:20:11,189
