404
00:20:11,189 --> 00:20:13,629
will secretly be meeting his brother soon.

405
00:20:13,629 --> 00:20:16,929
I want you to stake the place out like always.

406
00:20:16,929 --> 00:20:20,929
I want Officer Sato who was pursuing this case to stake out with...

407
00:20:20,929 --> 00:20:22,329
Me!

408
00:20:22,329 --> 00:20:24,229
Please let me do it!

409
00:20:25,529 --> 00:20:29,229
How unusual of you to say from your side that you'd like to stake out.

410
00:20:29,229 --> 00:20:31,209
Didn't you know

411
00:20:31,209 --> 00:20:33,629
