412
00:20:33,629 --> 00:20:35,213
Be on your guard.

413
00:20:35,213 --> 00:20:36,829
He's the younger brother of the suspect,

414
00:20:36,829 --> 00:20:38,929
but is said to be pretty violent.

415
00:20:38,929 --> 00:20:40,129
Yes, sir!

416
00:20:40,129 --> 00:20:42,329
-Be careful. -I will!

417
00:20:42,329 --> 00:20:45,223
What? Be careful?

418
00:20:48,929 --> 00:20:52,529
There's no movement at all?

419
00:20:52,529 --> 00:20:54,029
Inspector Sato.

420
00:20:56,729 --> 00:21:00,729
The name "Sato" is really common, isn't it?

421
00:21:02,429 --> 00:21:05,029
It's sure a nice name.

422
00:22:27,325 --> 00:22:28,929
This is Matsumoto.

423
00:22:28,929 --> 00:22:29,929
