00:23:17,729 --> 00:23:20,129
Hey, answer me, Matsumoto!

439
00:23:20,129 --> 00:23:21,729
Matsumoto! Matsumoto!

440
00:23:22,729 --> 00:23:24,329
Superintendent Matsumoto!

441
00:23:26,529 --> 00:23:28,029
Are you all right?

442
00:23:28,029 --> 00:23:30,629
You seem to have been having a bad dream.

443
00:23:30,629 --> 00:23:35,393
I'm sorry, I must've dozed off a bit.

444
00:23:35,393 --> 00:23:39,397
I think you should go home and get some rest at times.

445
00:23:39,629 --> 00:23:41,929
You've been sleeping over here for the past few days

446
00:23:41,929 --> 00:23:43,401
and haven't been getting much sleep, have you?

447
00:23:43,401 --> 00:23:45,929
I can't afford to rest just yet.

448
00:23:45,929 --> 00:23:47,729
There's only a week left

449
00:23:47,729 --> 00:23:50,429
before the time for the serial killing case expires.

450
00:23:50,429 --> 00:23:52,429
Even as we sit here like this,

451
00:23:52,429 --> 00:23:56,429
the hands of the clock are ticking away.

452
00:24:01,920 --> 00:24:04,292
Next Conan's Hint:

453
00:24:04,292 --> 00:24:05,780
"Nickname".

454
00:24:06,140 --> 00:24:08,224
Just as expected of Detective Queen Sonoko.

455
00:24:08,224 --> 00:24:10,300
And the Dance Queen as well, you know.

